ns:common.topic.description: PL/Java is a free add-on module that brings Java™ Stored Procedures, Triggers, and Functions to the PostgreSQL™ backend. The development started late 2003 and the first release of PL/Java arrived in January 2005. The project is released under the Berkley/BSD license.
